{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a harrowing journey with Alice, a college student, and her classmate Adrian, as they venture to a desolate town in search of a special cave. Uncover the chilling mystery surrounding Alice's strange nightmares and their connection to the town. The horror awaits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story</strong>: A deeply narrative-driven horror game. The story being the primary focus of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzles</strong>: Intuitive puzzles designed to engage without frustrating. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Music</strong>: A nostalgic soundtrack inspired by early 2000s gaming classics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Solo Developer</strong>: A solo developer's first game, with a few playtesters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHAPTERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game offers 7 to 15 hours of gameplay, depending on reading speed and engagement with optional content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Warning: Chapters 1-3 include puzzles, Chapter 4 features quick-time events, and the final chapter leans more towards a visual novel style with some quick-time events. The reasons for this structure delve into spoiler territory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- There are a total of 5 chapters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Chapters 1-4 each provide around 1-2 hours of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Chapter 5 offers a longer experience, lasting approximately 3 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999910/extras/sitti